channel.title: Can someone please please please! tell me how to put my server online?
channel.description:
:( :( :( i followed a tutorial like 10 times, did everything right, i got a no ip, my server is called sweetpkscape.no-ip.biz, but i dont know how to put it online, because i cant just go on mopar and play it! someone plz help me with whatever im doing wrong..
ive worked for 3 hours trying to fix it :(

item.title: Can someone please please please! tell me how to put my server online?
item.dc:creator: @Pur3_G3_Pk3r Pur3_G3_Pk3r
item.description:
@Pur3_G3_Pk3r wrote:

[quote=“r e d b u l l, post:5, topic:115527”]ok, is there anything i have to do in order to put it online?? it just doesnt make sense to log onto MY SEVER with out me even doing anything to put it ONLINE[br][size=1]Posted on: June 23, 2007, 11:27:59 AM[/size][hr]plz…[br][size=1]Posted on: June 23, 2007, 11:36:24 AM[/size][hr]omg[br][size=1]Posted on: June 23, 2007, 11:41:53 AM[/size][hr]OMFG!!![/quote] MATE! relax

1). Get a source

2). Forward your port to the port of the server/source

3). go to www.no-ip.com and make a domain there

4). connect to the ip u made on No-ip… (NOTE IF U GOT DYNAMIC IP U CANT DO IT) unless u do it on 10000 ips
